'''全球无神论者大会'''（又称无神论的兴起）是由{{le|澳大利亚无神论者基金会|Atheist Foundation of Australia}}和[[国际无神论联盟|国际无神论联盟]]赞助的[[无神论者|无神论者]]国际会议。

==第一届==
第一届在2010年3月12日至14日之间在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[墨尔本|墨尔本]]会展中心举行。大约2500名代表出席会议，所有门票在会议举行前五周即告售罄。<ref>{{Cite press release| title = Global Atheist Convention - Sold out!| publisher = 澳大利亚无神论者基金会| date = 30 January 2010| url = http://www.atheistfoundation.org.au/media-releases/global-atheist-convention-sold-out| accessdate = 19 February 2010| archive-date = 2010-09-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100917072224/http://atheistfoundation.org.au/media-releases/global-atheist-convention-sold-out| dead-url = no}}</ref>

会议主讲人包括有进化生物学家和畅销书作者[[理查德·道金斯|理查德·道金斯]], 还有[[Catherine_Deveny|Catherine Deveny]], [[Phillip_Adams|Phillip Adams]], [[塔斯利马·纳斯林|塔斯利马·纳斯林]], [[彼得·辛格|彼得·辛格]], [[PZ_Myers|PZ Myers]], [[Dan_Barker|Dan Barker]], [[Stuart_Bechman|Stuart Bechman]], [[Sue-Ann_Post|Sue-Ann Post]], [[Kylie_Sturgess|Kylie Sturgess]], John Perkins, [[Tamas_Pataki|Tamas Pataki]], [[Max_Wallace|Max Wallace]], [[Russell_Blackford|Russell Blackford]], [[Ian_Robinson_(rationalist)|Ian Robinson]], [[AC_Grayling|AC Grayling]], [[Robyn_Williams|Robyn Williams]], [[Simon_Taylor|Simon Taylor]], NonStampCollector, [[Craig_Reucassel|Craig Reucassel]],[[Julian_Morrow|Julian Morrow]]. <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.atheistconvention.org.au |title=The Rise of Atheism Website |author=Global Atheist Convention |date=2010 |accessdate=19 February 2010 |archive-date=2010-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100126050159/http://www.atheistconvention.org.au/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

